Package model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BasicCard
    An object representing a card, containing different Question object
    BasicSpecialCard
    A Basic SpecialCard, which is not used only once in the board.
    Board
    A representation of the board of the game
    Deck
    An object representing a Deck, containing different BasicCard object
    FinishCard
    A SpecialCard which is used at the end of the game.
    Game
    A representation of a game.
    GameOperation
    A class in charge of the conduct of a game and of it's animations
    Player
    An object representing a player.
    Position
    An object representing a position in a 2D plane
    Question
    An object representing a Question
    SpecialCard
    An abstract Class which is used in the DP Template method.
    Square
    An representation of a square, a small part of a Board
    StartCard
    A SpecialCard which is used at the start of the game.
